data.description: Introducing a charming home in the Parkwood Subdivision! This well-maintained gem boasts 1,638 square feet of comfortable living space, offering 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms. The property is in fantastic condition, showcasing a perfect blend of comfort and style.     Nestled on a nice-sized lot, you'll have plenty of room for outdoor activities and gardening. Enjoy the benefits of residing in a great neighborhood , conveniently  located near a highly-rated school, making it an ideal choice. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home and experience the best of living! Vacant and Ready for New Owner!
